   "info" : "<table width=\"100%\" summary=\"page for koch\"><tr><td>koch</td><td style=\"text-align: right;\">R Documentation</td></tr></table>\\n<h2>Ordinal Data from Koch</h2>\\n<h3>Description</h3>\\n<p>The <code>koch</code> data frame has 288 rows and 4 columns.\\n</p>\\n<h3>Usage</h3>\\n<pre>data(koch)</pre>\\n<h3>Format</h3>\\n<p>This data frame contains the following columns:\\n</p>\\n<dl>\\n<dt>trt</dt><dd><p>a numeric vector</p>\\n</dd>\\n<dt>day</dt><dd><p>a numeric vector</p>\\n</dd>\\n<dt>y</dt><dd><p>an ordered factor with levels:\\n<code>1</code> &lt; <code>2</code> &lt; <code>3</code></p>\\n</dd>\\n<dt>id</dt><dd><p>a numeric vector</p>\\n</dd>\\n</dl>\\n<h3>Examples</h3>\\n<pre>\\ndata(koch)\\nfit &lt;- ordgee(ordered(y) ~ trt + as.factor(day), id=id, data=koch, corstr=\"exch\")\\nsummary(fit)\\n</pre>\\n",
